{"tid":1535221,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"就係你班仆街唔跳閘","createTime":"2019-09-03T09:31:57.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-03T16:20:32.000Z","uid":316967,"like":8,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"dee6b1091dbcb6dd7c6738a8f1f887dfae80ffef","tid":1535221,"uid":316967,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T09:31:57.000Z","msg":"黨鐵先咁撚多錢<br />\n黨鐵就會覺得垃圾香港人無論點香港人都會比錢坐車<br />\n所以<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">全民跳閘！</span></span><br />\n我之前都唔敢跳，但琴日見到兩條女都跳，我即該又跳埋一份<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">爽到仆街</span></span><br />\n比狗拉又唔驚，驚比黨鐵查飛狗捉？<br />\n好撚多黨鐵職員見到都唔理你<br />\n唔敢跳既巴絲就跟人尾唔拍卡入閘囉！<br />\n總之<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">唔撚比錢黨鐵阿！</span></span>"},{"pid":"cbb57980ce032243d792c6745d7bf2708cc59dbf","tid":1535221,"uid":123991,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T09:32:09.000Z","msg":"<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>9月7日 (六) 1PM<br />\n機場交通壓力測試 (重考)</strong></div><br />\n<br />\n香港市民：<br />\n✅ 以遊客身份入機場觀賞飛機升降 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n✅ 唔識路就坐多幾轉車 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/cook.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n✅ 必需繳付車資乘坐黨鐵<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n其他國藉居民：<br />\n各有各做, 自由發揮 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/nyixFQQ.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FnyixFQQ.png&h=cc1f24a6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>9月8日 (日) 2PM<br />\n香港人權與民主法案集會<br />\n美國駐港澳總領事館</strong></div><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/2GKH20p.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F2GKH20p.png&h=6178433f&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"814f7ecfbf177b1b2935bb2a6537514c4dcf0903","tid":1535221